items.title: Chinese battery giant CATL posts annual revenue drop ahead of Hong Kong listing

items.title: BMW posts 37% drop in annual net profit, warns of 'subdued' Chinese demand
items.description: BMW's net profits slumped by more than a third in 2024 as weaker demand in China and Germany weighed on the high-end car manufacturer.
